      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed; acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3.",
      "rationale": "Blood viscosity and density values sourced from published literature for bovine blood at 37°C. Sensitivity of NIH to ±10% variation in viscosity was qualitatively noted but not formally quantified."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
