    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors met or exceeded their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The six non-assessed factors were confirmed acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted for identification of worst-case operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. This model has been applied in clinical research contexts where hemolysis risk stratification informs device design decisions.",
